==English==
===Alternative spellings===
* [[MacTard]]

===Etymology===
Blend of [[Mac]] and [[retard]].  Cf. [[tard]]. 

===Noun===
'''Mactard''' ''(plural:'' '''Mactards''')
# ''(slang, pejorative)'' A user or advocate of Macintosh computers, regarded as a stupid person.

